      "range": "1828-1853",
      "markText": "读书并不会让人更有智慧，它只是让愚蠢看起来更体面。",
      "totalCount": 1176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1828&rangeEnd=1853",
