    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300148782_7_567-600",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "567-600",
      "markText": "内在蓬勃旺盛的生命力所带来的愉悦，足以抵消人类所面临的痛苦与艰难。",
      "totalCount": 884,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=567&rangeEnd=600",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25332040813aba09eg0127be?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=567&rangeEnd=600"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300148782_10_4430-4496",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4430-4496",
      "markText": "大多数人穷尽一生，唯一的成就不过是为自己的后代建造起屋舍，储备好粮食；而他们的后代来到世间，也不过是重复着与祖辈完全相同的乏味劳作。",
      "totalCount": 756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4430&rangeEnd=4496",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25332040813aba09eg0127be?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4430&rangeEnd=4496"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300148782_6_606-790",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "606-790",
      "markText": "就是让人心胸狭隘。 他们变得斤斤计较、怨天尤人， 对任何微不足道的小事都异常敏感。 若说苦难能使人品格高尚， 那纯粹是无稽之谈。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=606&rangeEnd=790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25332040813aba09eg0127be?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=606&rangeEnd=790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300148782_16_2047-2100",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2047-2100",
      "markText": "年轻人被渴望融入群体的焦虑折磨得痛苦不堪，而中年人之所以可以自得其乐，恰恰是因为他们终于与自己达成了和解。",
      "totalCount": 558,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2047&rangeEnd=2100",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25332040813aba09eg0127be?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2047&rangeEnd=2100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300148782_9_5396-5471",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5396-5471",
      "markText": "爱情之事最妙的是节制。没有人能无休止地爱下去。如果爱情太过顺利，毫无阻碍，那么迎接你的必然是无可挽回的厌倦。最持久的爱情，莫过于从未得到满足的那一种。",
      "totalCount": 546,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5396&rangeEnd=5471",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25332040813aba09eg0127be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5396&rangeEnd=5471"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300148782_12_987-1087",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "987-1087",
      "markText": "生命的终结，就像在黄昏里读一本书。最初你全然沉浸其中，丝毫未觉光阴流逝；突然之间，书页上的字迹变得难以辨认，你抬起头来，才发现暮色已然降临，黑暗无声地吞噬了一切，再也看不清那些刚才还意味深长的字句了。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300148782&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=987&rangeEnd=1087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25332040813aba09eg0127be?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=987&rangeEnd=1087"
    },
    {
